# Going Platform - Environment Configuration Guide

## Overview
Complete environment setup for the Going Platform with all services, integrations, and monitoring tools.

---

## 1. Core Services

### API Gateway
```env
# API Gateway Configuration
API_GATEWAY_PORT=3000
API_GATEWAY_HOST=0.0.0.0
NODE_ENV=production
LOG_LEVEL=info

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=60
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=1000
REDIS_RATE_LIMIT_PREFIX=rate_limit

# Cache
CACHE_ENABLED=true
CACHE_TTL=3600
REDIS_CACHE_PREFIX=cache

# WebSocket & CORS Configuration
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001
WEBSOCKET_CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:3001
WEBSOCKET_CORS_CREDENTIALS=true
```

### Microservices
```env
# Service Configuration
RIDE_SERVICE_PORT=3001
PAYMENT_SERVICE_PORT=3002
USER_SERVICE_PORT=3003
NOTIFICATION_SERVICE_PORT=3004

# Service Communication
SERVICE_DISCOVERY_ENABLED=true
EUREKA_SERVER_URL=http://eureka:8761/eureka
```

---

## 2. Database Configuration

### MongoDB
```env
# MongoDB Connection
MONGODB_URL=mongodb://mongodb:27017/going-platform
MONGODB_USER=admin
MONGODB_PASSWORD=your_secure_password_here
MONGODB_AUTH_DB=admin

# MongoDB Replication
MONGODB_REPLICA_SET=rs0
MONGODB_POOL_SIZE=50
MONGODB_POOL_MIN_SIZE=10
MONGODB_POOL_TIMEOUT=30000

# Query Monitoring
MONGODB_SLOW_QUERY_THRESHOLD=200
MONGODB_ENABLE_PROFILING=true
```

### Redis
```env
# Redis Connection
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_DB=0
REDIS_PASSWORD=your_redis_password

# Redis Cluster (if applicable)
REDIS_CLUSTER_ENABLED=false
REDIS_CLUSTER_NODES=redis-1:6379,redis-2:6379,redis-3:6379

# Redis Configuration
REDIS_MAX_RETRIES=3
REDIS_RETRY_DELAY=1000
REDIS_TIMEOUT=5000

# Cache Strategy
REDIS_EVICTION_POLICY=allkeys-lru
REDIS_MAX_MEMORY=1gb
```

---

## 3. Observability & Monitoring

### Sentry Configuration
```env
# Sentry Error Tracking
SENTRY_DSN=https://your_key@sentry.io/your_project_id
SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=production
SENTRY_RELEASE=1.0.0
SENTRY_ENABLED=true
SENTRY_TRACES_SAMPLE_RATE=0.1
SENTRY_PROFILES_SAMPLE_RATE=0.1

# Alert Configuration
SENTRY_ALERT_THRESHOLD_CRITICAL=5
SENTRY_ALERT_THRESHOLD_HIGH=20
SENTRY_ALERT_THRESHOLD_MEDIUM=100
```

### PagerDuty Integration
```env
# PagerDuty Configuration
PAGERDUTY_ENABLED=true
PAGERDUTY_API_KEY=your_pagerduty_api_key
PAGERDUTY_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id
PAGERDUTY_ESCALATION_POLICY_ID=your_escalation_policy_id
PAGERDUTY_INTEGRATION_KEY=your_integration_key

# Incident Management
PAGERDUTY_AUTO_RESOLVE_TIMEOUT=3600
PAGERDUTY_ESCALATION_DELAY_MINUTES=5
```

### Slack Integration
```env
# Slack Configuration
SLACK_ENABLED=true
SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-your-bot-token
SLACK_APP_TOKEN=xapp-your-app-token
SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET=your_signing_secret

# Alert Channels
SLACK_INCIDENT_CRITICAL=#incident-critical
SLACK_INCIDENT_HIGH=#incident-high
SLACK_INCIDENT_MEDIUM=#incident-medium
SLACK_INCIDENT_LOW=#incident-low
SLACK_GENERAL=#alerts

# Message Settings
SLACK_THREAD_REPLIES=true
SLACK_MENTION_ON_CRITICAL=true
SLACK_MENTION_USERS=@on-call,@team-lead
```

### Prometheus & Grafana
```env
# Prometheus Configuration
PROMETHEUS_ENABLED=true
PROMETHEUS_PORT=9090
PROMETHEUS_SCRAPE_INTERVAL=15s
PROMETHEUS_EVALUATION_INTERVAL=15s
PROMETHEUS_RETENTION_DAYS=30

# Metrics Collection
METRICS_ENABLED=true
METRICS_PORT=9091
METRICS_PREFIX=going_platform_

# Grafana Configuration
GRAFANA_ENABLED=true
GRAFANA_PORT=3100
GRAFANA_ADMIN_USER=admin
GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD=your_secure_password
GRAFANA_DEFAULT_DATASOURCE=Prometheus
```

### ELK Stack
```env
# Elasticsearch Configuration
ELASTICSEARCH_HOST=elasticsearch
ELASTICSEARCH_PORT=9200
ELASTICSEARCH_USERNAME=elastic
ELASTICSEARCH_PASSWORD=your_password
ELASTICSEARCH_INDEX_PREFIX=going-platform
ELASTICSEARCH_RETENTION_DAYS=30

# Logstash Configuration
LOGSTASH_HOST=logstash
LOGSTASH_PORT=5000
LOGSTASH_ENABLED=true

# Kibana Configuration
KIBANA_HOST=kibana
KIBANA_PORT=5601
```

