## 4. Security Configuration

### JWT & Authentication
```env
# JWT Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_min_32_characters
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=24h
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your_refresh_token_secret
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# OAuth2 (if using)
OAUTH_ENABLED=false
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret
```

### Vulnerability Scanning
```env
# OWASP Dependency Check
DEPENDENCY_CHECK_ENABLED=true
DEPENDENCY_CHECK_THRESHOLD=HIGH

# Snyk Configuration
SNYK_ENABLED=true
SNYK_TOKEN=your_snyk_api_token
SNYK_ORG_ID=your_org_id

# SonarQube Configuration
SONARQUBE_ENABLED=true
SONAR_HOST_URL=http://sonarqube:9000
SONAR_LOGIN=your_sonar_token
SONAR_PROJECT_KEY=going-platform
```

### Secret Scanning
```env
# GitGuardian Integration
GITGUARDIAN_ENABLED=true
GITGUARDIAN_API_KEY=your_gitguardian_api_key

# Secret Detection
SECRET_SCANNING_ENABLED=true
SECRETS_VAULT_URL=http://vault:8200
SECRETS_VAULT_TOKEN=your_vault_token
```

