## 9. Development & Testing

### Development Configuration
```env
# Development Settings
DEBUG=true
MOCK_EXTERNAL_SERVICES=false
SEED_DATABASE=false

# Logging
LOG_FORMAT=json
LOG_INCLUDE_STACK_TRACE=true
LOG_INCLUDE_REQUEST_ID=true
```

### Testing Configuration
```env
# Test Database
TEST_MONGODB_URL=mongodb://mongodb-test:27017/going-platform-test
TEST_REDIS_URL=redis://redis-test:6379/1

# Test Settings
TEST_TIMEOUT=30000
TEST_SEED_DATA=true
TEST_CLEANUP_AFTER=true
```

